{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "瓦莱里奥 第3话 此剑应当守护之物",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "真好吃♪主厨的炖蔬菜最棒啦！\\n对吧？瓦莱里奥？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "……里奥……瓦莱里奥！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "哇啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "真是的……再不吃要凉了哦？\\n你最近总是心不在焉的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "啊……抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "你是在想国事……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "虽然父王不肯告诉我具体情况，\\n但局势一定不利吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "自从战争开始以后，\\n我也被禁止去街上走动了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "街上遇到的那些孩子们……\\n不知道怎么样了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当天晚上\\n瓦莱里奥的房间",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "唉……让公主殿下担心了……\\n我到底在干什么啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "（正如公主殿下所说，我国正处于劣势。\\n要是输掉这场战争，这个国家……\\n还有公主殿下会变成什么样。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "我要继续袖手旁观吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "（现在待在公主殿下身边，\\n真的能保护公主殿下吗？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "（在前线挥剑杀敌，为国家带来胜利。\\n这才是为了国家的将来……\\n为了保护公主殿下吧？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "我……要怎么办……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "是谁！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "刚才……有人站在门前？\\n不，是错觉吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "为了让他打起精神，\\n我还吩咐主厨做了宵夜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "也对……瓦莱里奥想要的\\n根本就不是什么料理。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "（其实我心里很清楚。\\n瓦莱里奥想要的到底是什么……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "（他总是看着遍体鳞伤的士兵\\n露出一副不甘心的表情。\\n还经常望着窗外……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "就算心里清楚，也不想放他走。\\n因为我怕他会死……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "可是，身为公主的我这样……\\n根本就没法保护国家啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "我得快点长大……变得更强大……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "国王",
            "context": "瓦莱里奥，你来啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "是的。今天所为何事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "国王",
            "context": "嗯。从今天起，\\n交给你一个新任务。\\n我要你再次率领青骑队。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "什么！？为什么！\\n普莉米亚公主怎么说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "是我……点名要你的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "是我点名要你来当队长的。\\n我跟父王说\\n瓦莱里奥应该在战场上杀敌。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "公主……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "但是……我希望你能答应我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "你会平安归来，再当我的骑士。\\n你能答应我吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "是……我一定做到。\\n我一定会回到公主殿下身边！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "国王",
            "context": "那么……瓦莱里奥。\\n你即刻奔赴前线，跟青骑队会合。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "加油啊，瓦莱里奥……\\n要保护好这个国家……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵1",
            "context": "兵力减少了好多啊……\\n我们接下来，会怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵2",
            "context": "我们要是在这里退缩了，国家就……\\n所以我们不能退缩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵1",
            "context": "但是……光凭我们真的能保护好吗？\\n没有了那个人的带领……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我不是告诉过你们……\\n不准在战场上闲聊吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵1",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵1",
            "context": "你是……\\n为什么会在这里！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "我接到了王命。\\n从今天起，青骑队又归我率领了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵2",
            "context": "真、真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵1",
            "context": "太好了……真是太好了！\\n只要有你在……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "你们都给我听好了。\\n上了战场就要豁出命去战斗，\\n但是要给我活着回来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "要誓死守卫\\n我们的缅萨拉圣国！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "跟着队长冲啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "敌兵",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事？\\n那些家伙的动作\\n和昨天仿佛不是同一支军队……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "都跟着我来！带着倒下的队友\\n那份遗志一起！冲啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01",
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵们",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦莱里奥",
            "context": "（我一定要用这把剑带来胜利，\\n然后履行诺言。我会保护好公主！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "凭借着瓦莱里奥的活跃，\\n缅萨拉军不仅扭转了战局，\\n甚至逐渐转守为攻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110295_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "与此同时，\\n在王城等待骑士归来的公主……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "我吃完了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "公主殿下？又剩下这么多……\\n是饭菜不合您的口味吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "我吃不出味道……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "吃不出味道？什么意思……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "普莉米亚",
            "context": "不知道……看起来……\\n明明……这么……好吃……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "公主殿下！？公主殿下！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}